rComments: This rating is coming form a Physics-Maths student. His classes are never a dull moment. He's able to get all the class to interact with him and with each other. However if you want to do really with him and this class, maybe come prepared with just more the high school level Spanish. BUT THE TEXT BOOK because he barely has notes.

He was super funny, and is very approachable, but during lectures it was really hard to understand him. He talks super fast, and moves super fast. He makes it interesting, but confusing at the same time. Midterm wasn't hard.
The class is very interesting but I had a lot of trouble understanding him. He is not very helpful and moves super quickly. He made class as fun as he could and encouraged us all.
